TASKNAME=Run a Python script and verify its successful execution.
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if exists the file ~/agent_test/hello.py.
TASKCOMMAND=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo create a python file called ~/agent_test/hello.py that display the string 'Hello world!'. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.   
TASKVERIFY=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo execute the program ~/agent_test/hello.py.
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if exists the file ~/agent_test/hello.py.
